{
  "stem": "13673.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And to  tell  you the truth, to this day, I think, there's part of me that is different.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's not necessarily a good thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I sometimes would like to be not so different, but there you are.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was always thin and short, and I didn't think I was particularly beautiful.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never will be.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I didn't have a very good image, coming to think of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only the letters that I wrote.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know why I didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wish I could sometimes turn the clock back just for that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wouldn't really, though.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had-- I enjoyed my music lessons a lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was learning the piano.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had taken cello in-- lessons in Germany, and that stopped after two years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then in England, I got piano lessons, and I did enjoy that a lot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I-- and I was very-- I was becoming extremely religious and rather evan-- evangelical.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember trying to convert my brother, or-- or at least to, you know, open something up with my brother, and  he got very concerned.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't really react to me at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What I-- he might have written something to my parents, but I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were trying to get out of Germany seriously now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, my father had been released from Dachau on the promise to start arranging his rel-- his leaving Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And having said that, they also didn't make it easy for him to leave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And his-- his bank accounts were locked up, and he couldn't get to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The business was sold for a pittance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- the money wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Plus, he couldn't get a visa to go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
